{"tid":1787610,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"恩怨情仇：球場到社會積怨逾三十載","createTime":"2019-12-18T05:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T05:15:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0859e164d5b9aedbbf587335a0cefd2da1c41144","tid":1787610,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191218/6FB5LRGGHXQ3LHAHVUPBNRQEJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191218%2F6FB5LRGGHXQ3LHAHVUPBNRQEJU%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=c76338e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191218%2F6FB5LRGGHXQ3LHAHVUPBNRQEJU%2F&h=c5b014ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191218/6FB5LRGGHXQ3LHAHVUPBNRQEJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n恩怨情仇：球場到社會積怨逾三十載<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576595824_e882.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576595824_e882.gif&h=baf84dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中港歷來在世盃外對陣四次，除1982年那屆外，之後三次，86、2006及18年也掀起兩地足球恩怨，以至社會紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n繼82年對壘後，港隊在86年再與中國同組，同組有弱旅汶萊及澳門，港隊與國足經過五戰，戰績同為4勝1和，外圍賽最後一戰港隊在85年5月19日作客北京對中國，最終港隊憑張志德及顧錦輝建功，以2:1贏波，最終壓過中國小組出線，北京市賽後因中國出局而暴動，這是港足史上最重要勝仗，人稱「五一九事件」。<br />\n<br />\n06世盃外，已出局的港隊最後一戰作客中國，范俊業救出鄭智12碼，最終港隊輸0:7，中國因一個得球之差不及科威特出局，范俊業成為「中國罪人」。<br />\n<br />\n18世盃外，港中同列C組後，中國足協發佈以「不輕視任何對手」為主題系列海報，這張海報不單涉種族歧視，更帶輕視，將兩地矛盾表面化，激起球迷在國際賽前狂噓國歌，此舉一直維持至今。<br />\n<br />\n港足15年9月3日作客中國，全場中國隊有40次攻門，但最終0:0完場。中國隊長鄭智比賽期間疑向倒地的葉鴻輝吐口水，鄭智事後否認。同年11月17日在旺角場上演的「港中大戰」，港球迷高舉「BOO」及「HONG KONG IS NOT CHINA」標語，繼續狂噓國歌，全城打氣下港隊再0:0和中國。<br />\n<br />\n記者：曾雁平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576595825_386e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576595825_386e.jpg&h=09962337&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72a8ca9d06519f5393468b9442a086bf93fe9be3","tid":1787610,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb96b7eaf7802b3df65695e4984b9d8971db2e7f","tid":1787610,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:12:23.000Z","msg":"今晚又上演大戰<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74ca2cbf28ee37279aba65090385a217d886a81","tid":1787610,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb96b7eaf7802b3df65695e4984b9d8971db2e7f","tid":1787610,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:12:23.000Z","msg":"今晚又上演大戰<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"15：15<br />\n晏晝"}]}